{"tid":1018467,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸流亡人士 獲香港電影金像獎提名","createTime":"2019-02-12T09:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T01:04:17.000Z","uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e561f54eca85282490748d54d31863c3843114","tid":1018467,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190212/59248049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190212%2F59248049&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuipZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=16927e83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190212%2F59248049&h=10e259f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190212/59248049</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月12日 <br />\n【金像獎提名】《自由行》入圍最佳編劇 導演應亮被迫流亡香港至今<br />\n<br />\n本屆香港電影金像獎其中一套入圍最佳編劇的作品《自由行》，由旅居香港的大陸導演應亮執導。去年他已憑本片入圍第71屆瑞士盧卡諾影展（Locarno Festival）。能夠入圍金像獎，他以短訊回應說：「恭喜兩位合作編劇陳慧和三三！假設沒有她們，《自由行》無法真地完成表達。過往半年，《自由行》與世界各地的觀眾見了面，只有中國沒可能放映。一部電影可以「行」去的地方很多，但能停留下來的地方很少，香港肯定是其中一個令《自由行》安身的地方。感謝香港電影金像獎，把《自由行》這個名字，留在香港電影的歷史當中！」<br />\n<br />\n《自》片以應亮自身遭遇作藍本，故事講述流亡香港的大陸女導演楊樞，跟四川的母親只能透過網絡見面，她想在母親胃癌手術前，二人可以親身見面。最後她借參加電影節，母親參加旅行團，希望一家人最終能在台灣團聚。可惜母親不能脫離旅行團「自由行」，最後要訂相同的酒店、查好旅行團路線，楊樞一家三口，才能在酒店和各風景區團聚。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應亮早在12年，憑第一部長片《我還有話要說》贏過盧卡諾影展的最佳導演獎。《我》片取材自08年大陸造成6人死亡的「楊佳襲警案」。因被指損害國家形象，應亮被迫流亡香港至今。</strong>居港七年已取得香港永久居民身份證。《自》為他第二部長片，全片在台灣拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n最佳編劇入圍名單：<br />\n1.陳慧、三三、應亮《自由行》<br />\n2.林超賢《紅海行動》<br />\n3.陳詠燊《逆流大叔》<br />\n4.陳小娟《淪落人》<br />\n5.莊文強《無雙》"},{"pid":"6e0e6a4c130d8051e613d9b634d1b1869dab1b31","tid":1018467,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8985e2931e6b12301ecfd17c94cc72c4111f200","tid":1018467,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be912b77867eafc5ab8262674d5e4fbece79810","tid":1018467,"uid":164965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"流亡黎香港係咪等坐洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2634e1af89961d9e9f0f6d189b63a8467e1a208c","tid":1018467,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be912b77867eafc5ab8262674d5e4fbece79810","tid":1018467,"uid":164965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"流亡黎香港係咪等坐洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"想知佢係咪真係相信「一國兩制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfd0aed857bc5db8461729d475042354fb1c6c8","tid":1018467,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2634e1af89961d9e9f0f6d189b63a8467e1a208c","tid":1018467,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be912b77867eafc5ab8262674d5e4fbece79810","tid":1018467,"uid":164965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"流亡黎香港係咪等坐洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"想知佢係咪真係相信「一國兩制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a3e417889f50289d8a47b8d118bf56cd945b3d","tid":1018467,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}